<plot>This short film won both the Jury Award and Audience Award for the Good Morning America 2004 "I See Scary Movies" Contest. It is a mock infomercial that will teach you how to avoid the common pitfalls associated with being stuck in a horror movie. It was shot in one day on a Canon XL1, and edited in Final Cut Pro 3. The score was created using Apple's Soundtrack.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?402033</url></doc>
